    "description": "逃离腐朽贵族的魔爪，摆脱阻止他们撤退的恶魔。你要时刻保持安静，躲在黑暗的阴影里，面对残暴独裁的国度以及那个自称要帮助你的神秘女人，去揭开他们不可告人的秘密。这是一款富有剧情的逼真的隐身类恐怖游戏。去找出那些夺走你一切的人的谎言和秘密，让古老的国度恢复昔日的荣耀。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >隐藏于黑暗中</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594200/extras/c7c372b01880242cb8b27a18e8b22d99.poster.avif?t=1710562966\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594200/extras/c7c372b01880242cb8b27a18e8b22d99.webm?t=1710562966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594200/extras/c7c372b01880242cb8b27a18e8b22d99.mp4?t=1710562966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>充分利用逼真的隐身机制，例如隐藏在黑暗区域避免被发现。<br>如果你躲在黑暗中，恶魔将无法看到你，除非他离得很近。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >潜行</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594200/extras/d58d0633ebaaa6e5368caca8b2f8cca6.poster.avif?t=1710562966\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594200/extras/d58d0633ebaaa6e5368caca8b2f8cca6.webm?t=1710562966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594200/extras/d58d0633ebaaa6e5368caca8b2f8cca6.mp4?t=1710562966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>当你走在安静的表面，比如地毯上时，恶魔不会听到你的声音，除非你靠得太近。你也可以通过蹲下悄悄的溜过去避免被发现。<br>如果你发出太多声音，恶魔会立即开始追赶你。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >破解真相</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594200/extras/9cc7341f26363d74d42dee203c3b96cd.poster.avif?t=1710562966\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594200/extras/9cc7341f26363d74d42dee203c3b96cd.webm?t=1710562966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594200/extras/9cc7341f26363d74d42dee203c3b96cd.mp4?t=1710562966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>检查以前住在解放湖的居民留下的笔记。你是一个囚犯，你以前从未来过这里。所以你不会找到任何线索或者提示，地图甚至地图标记。<br>根据你所发现的秘密，你将会有不同的结局。你会把这些结局全部体验一遍吗?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >解放黑暗世界</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594200/extras/be4f7f2fcd93dc4bb85cf28a22dc3281.poster.avif?t=1710562966\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594200/extras/be4f7f2fcd93dc4bb85cf28a22dc3281.webm?t=1710562966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594200/extras/be4f7f2fcd93dc4bb85cf28a22dc3281.mp4?t=1710562966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>黑暗恶魔夺走了你所爱的一切，是时候揭露真相了。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 面向喜欢类似 <i>《失忆症 Amnesia》</i>这一类隐身类恐怖游戏的玩家，以及喜欢角色驱动的剧情类玩家。<br></li><li> 逼真的隐身机制，包括使用阴影保持隐蔽，以及在安静的表面行进来保持不被发现。<br></li><li> 采用黑暗系的细致入微的情节设定，以及扣人心弦的极具神秘感的叙述方式。<br></li><li> 仅由一名开发独立完成制作。</li></ul>",
